productsList.title: Fax Out
productsList.description:
Send fax straight from your device! Features a built-in document scanner, document reader and a signature tool. Pay as you go – no monthly fees or small print!

Fax Out is a simple and easy to use tool for sending fax from your Windows 10 device. 

Use its smart document scanner with an automatic paper detection to fax physical documents or open any existing docx, odt, pdf, jpg and many more. You can also write a new fax from scratch directly on a blank page within the app. What you see is what you get.

Need to fill out a form prior to faxing? You can do it with this app! Use the text, pen, marker and a signature tool to make all the necessary adjustments.

How to send your fax?
1.	Download the app
2.	Create your Vanaia account
3.	Purchase desired number of Fax Tokens (a single fax token can also be purchased as app's add-on)
4.	Scan, import or write a fax
5.	Enter the number and tap send

Fax Out uses a prepaid balance model of Fax Tokens. 1 token = 1 page* 

(*sent to USA, Canada, Australia, most of Europe most of Asia. Some countries have higher tariffs; more details at developer's webpage )

productsList.title: GoFax
productsList.description:
Download the free GoFax® app today for mobile, tablet and desktop!

The GoFax® app is a secure and easy-way to send and receive fax and SMS from anywhere. With an intuitive and user-friendly dashboard, the GoFax® app is designed for flexible fax and SMS management for you and your team from office, at home or while on-the-go. 

Key Features:
• Quick Send – send fax and SMS quickly through the easy-to-use dashboard. 
• Capture documents via camera – simply take a photo of the document you need to fax and upload direct from your mobile device.
• Manage Inbox & Outbox – view sent and received fax and SMS messages and download or print received documents direct from the app. 
• Multiple Recipients - send fax or SMS messages to multiple recipients. 
• Cover Sheets - option to add cover sheets to faxes with built-in cover sheet option. 
• Fax Campaign Scheduling - set the desired date and time for future fax campaigns. 
• Standard or High Resolution - send your fax in standard or high quality (high quality incurs a 25% surcharge). 
• SMS Preview – preview your SMS, view character limit, parts and cost before the message is sent. 

Highlights:
• HIPAA Compliant – ensures security of protected health information (PHI) and meets industry standards for healthcare. 
• International Coverage - easily reach your audience with options to send fax and SMS internationally. 
• Stringent Security – multiple layers of data security in place to protect sensitive data including managed firewalls, encryptions and files stored on the cloud. 
• Transfer your Existing Fax Number – port your fax number to GoFax and access your existing fax number and incoming faxes direct to your app inbox. 

Setting up a new GoFax account:
To access the GoFax® app and the fax/ SMS service, you will need to have an existing GoFax account with send & receive plans and packages allocated to your account. To get started, please visit: www.gofax.com.au 
Contact us:
We're always excited to hear from you. if you have feedback, questions or concerns, please contact us at www.gofax.com.au/contact-us

productsList.title: VIFHE LMS
productsList.description:
Welcome to the official Learning Management System (LMS) app of the Virtual Institute for Higher Education (VIFHE). This app is designed exclusively for VIFHE’s enrolled students, educators and admin offering you the flexibility to access your learning resources anytime, anywhere.
With VIFHE LMS, students and educators can seamlessly access a range of features, including:

• Course Management – Easily organize, manage, and track courses with intuitive tools for content delivery and assessment.
• User Management – Simplify student and instructor enrollment, profiles, and roles with a centralized user system.
• Attendance Tracking – Keep attendance records accurate and up-to-date, ensuring students stay on track.
• Payment Management – Securely handle payments for courses, making it easy to manage tuition and fees.
• And More – Enjoy a wide array of additional features designed to create a seamless educational experience.

Empowering you to learn on the go, the VIFHE LMS app brings all your educational needs into one convenient platform.
